{"tid":444490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拒做樓奴】疑不滿業主拒退按金　情侶設「死魚大陣」養蛆蟲報復","createTime":"2017-10-22T14:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T03:25:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce69a73e9cad722e6911defca12ef139c573ac3","tid":444490,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171022/s00004/1508668842534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171022%2Fs00004%2F1508668842534&d=ytPBNWVX11MqgvXu93vcRS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d30093d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171022%2Fs00004%2F1508668842534&h=af5cd1cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171022/s00004/1508668842534</a><br />\n<br />\n一對外地情侶共租一個單位，早前提早退租，遭業主以合約早寫明為由拒絕發還按金。二人疑心生不滿，除了任由家貓通地大小二便外，更將死魚塞在假天花、雪櫃、花樽等陰暗地方，任其腐爛生蟲。一條又一條蛆蟲在惡臭充斥的房間中爬行，場面嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n業主聲稱今年5月租出單位，租予一對情侶一年。合約列明按金為4,500元人民，每月租金1,500元，每季首3日要支付3個月租金，如有人提早退租，按金不會退還；另外亦列明屋內不准飼養寵物。<br />\n<br />\n情侶上月突然提出退租並要求取回按金，業主回覆指：「雙方約定的租房時間未到，如果一定要退押金須找到其他人租住才可以。」此後，業主跟二人失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n直到日前，業主收到物業管理員致電通知，指有住客投訴其單位傳出刺鼻惡臭。業主到場發現，屋內曾有人養貓，遍地都是貓糧貓糞，地上還放有裝滿死魚的面盤。另外在雪櫃每一層、大花瓶、假天花縫隙等等位置，同樣可以見到死魚屍骸。<br />\n<br />\n部分死魚長滿蛆蟲，更可悲的是屋內傢俱及雪櫃縫隙已受蛆蟲入侵，整個雪櫃要報癈。業主說，由於單位太臭太可怕，沒有清潔工人願意幫忙清理。"},{"pid":"a9ab7bf2386a0ef5400b541d95ef8a14dc882c41","tid":444490,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce36b88b8ee7d8590a69bede2334838073e102c0","tid":444490,"uid":34336,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c82f7dda0781dc386698d0494ececde7777ddefb","tid":444490,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"租俾支那人 南亞人都係自己攞黎"},{"pid":"dba12ea8a408e78225806daca228f158ff3f58cd","tid":444490,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"留名等睇租客反告業主未得其同意，清走屋內的貓糧，等同偷竊罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e632d841f4601bee89ac072af533db78ec3e46d","tid":444490,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"廣西呀發生係<br />\n<br />\n港豬邊夠膽咁做"},{"pid":"db7ffaaf387a77acd5cdd835b4fe63fb9cf04493","tid":444490,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"支那狗係咁上下"},{"pid":"787ba84c51a088a45d0fc0984064c455962b359b","tid":444490,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外地</span>情侶?"},{"pid":"9ab28e1a59473041d436fae6df1e5089f089e577","tid":444490,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"專登cut走廣西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62da3bf0ee6b6698325cae527dae350c3656d793","tid":444490,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專登cut走廣西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到千五租都知唔係香港啦"},{"pid":"870300abcecb2df4c2158c84c1d8e50b1899750e","tid":444490,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打倒業主, 玩殘班炒樓撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把口反共，但愛共產主義？"}]}